data.text:
In 1989, Warner Bros. Feature Animation announced they will be making a film titled The Reef. Production started in 1992 and Universal Pictures would also distribute the film. But it was later cancelled in 1994 and scrapped in 1997.

Plot[]

The plot is unknown, but maybe most likely the same as Shark Tale.

Cast[]

Michael J. Fox as Jimmy (an early version of Oscar)

Why it was cancelled[]

The reason is unknown.
